{"tid":2173772,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"密晤特朗普 fb教主被指推動美國封殺TikTok","createTime":"2020-08-25T12:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T17:08:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"87e0c7e5783d98e1d69aed113a8d8cf49e802dc4","tid":2173772,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:23:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200825/VZ7YGEXL5VA5BB44O6BWOKKOTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200825%2FVZ7YGEXL5VA5BB44O6BWOKKOTE%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=bf5f16dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200825%2FVZ7YGEXL5VA5BB44O6BWOKKOTE%2F&h=bae87164\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200825/VZ7YGEXL5VA5BB44O6BWOKKOTE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n密晤特朗普 fb教主被指推動美國封殺TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_7dW_oy3nF839VaPOahHnLOy-z4=/960x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PGUOXRPKK5DIDBCGOAQ3WX5FEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_7dW_oy3nF839VaPOahHnLOy-z4%3D%2F960x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPGUOXRPKK5DIDBCGOAQ3WX5FEM.jpg&h=e7db0e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■朱克伯格被指是美國封殺TikTok推手。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\nTikTok由美國時興社交媒體變為美國重點打擊對象。美媒報道，TikTok對手、facebook創辦人兼行政總裁朱克伯格或扮演一定角色，指他去年秋天兩次到訪華盛頓，發表公開演講，私下與國會議員和總統特朗普會面，警告TikTok對美國價值及科技霸權構成危險。<br />\n<br />\n美國《華爾街日報》引述消息稱，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點名母企沒維護言論自由<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，朱克伯格和美國官員及國會議員會晤期間亦警告，中國科技公司對美國價值及美國在科技界的地位帶來威脅。他亦指，TikTok背後由總部位於北京的字節跳動（ByteDance）擁有，而字節跳動並沒有如facebook一樣致力於維護言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅周一表示，白宮對TikTok的政策上，朱克伯格的影響是零。 。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》/CNBC"},{"pid":"1e039d9754f09f3351aa3ded4df9bd817399f27a","tid":2173772,"uid":282757,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:27:00.000Z","msg":"敵人嘅敵人就係我地嘅朋友（暫時）"},{"pid":"71a18b8fdd143b494e892698775f8b5c1a61405b","tid":2173772,"uid":255637,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到勢頭唔對即轉向"},{"pid":"0d1cc5f5b8b21b0efe42ddb9c554190b8d056374","tid":2173772,"uid":45213,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:29:36.000Z","msg":"奶左咁多年都入唔到支那，而家仲要整件抖音來搶埋佢美國市場，唔搞你就笨柒啦"},{"pid":"79d2be74ab679f9f88f70a9aa358cece2266b2a0","tid":2173772,"uid":77180,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:33:35.000Z","msg":"無得奶共搞到變幫手滅共"},{"pid":"1ec16e57d42a25e7567a869fea681c7df12d9724","tid":2173772,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:34:33.000Z","msg":"原諒佢啦"},{"pid":"d03d66bc9d96f6bd87867b77cdfa4b36a97c525a","tid":2173772,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"79d2be74ab679f9f88f70a9aa358cece2266b2a0","tid":2173772,"uid":77180,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:33:35.000Z","msg":"無得奶共搞到變幫手滅共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:38:10.000Z","msg":"因愛成恨"},{"pid":"9442c1da9e566950199ac090671836c4a9770c3d","tid":2173772,"uid":110079,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0d1cc5f5b8b21b0efe42ddb9c554190b8d056374","tid":2173772,"uid":45213,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:29:36.000Z","msg":"奶左咁多年都入唔到支那，而家仲要整件抖音來搶埋佢美國市場，唔搞你就笨柒啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:03:54.000Z","msg":"支那就係咁 比少少甜頭引你入陷阱 <br />\n之後就加碼要求好多野先比返少少利益你<br />\n根本就係不平等交易"},{"pid":"05f5539b9d9b0aade45bd4947b5fd2ca5f14edc5","tid":2173772,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T14:04:41.000Z","msg":"朱閪百格生性"},{"pid":"d47f626708d1573ebe7b24a40c9304c971d64dd3","tid":2173772,"uid":143343,"like":6,"dislike":0,"s